{id:"api-2014-magic-items-feather-token-bird",name:"Bird Feather Token",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Bird Feather Token"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Category",content:"Wondrous Items"},{title:"Rarity",content:"Rare"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["Wondrous item, rare","This tiny object looks like a feather.","You can use an action to toss the token 5 feet into the air. The token disappears and an enormous, multicolored bird takes its place. The bird has the statistics of a roc, but it obeys your simple commands and can't attack. It can carry up to 500 pounds while flying at its maximum speed (16 miles an hour for a maximum of 144 miles per day, with a one-hour rest for every 3 hours of flying), or 1,000 pounds at half that speed. The bird disappears after flying its maximum distance for a day or if it drops to 0 hit points. You can dismiss the bird as an action."]}]}